ShinyGeoip,is,a,free,and,open,source,IP,to,geoloaction,API,The,API,accepts,a,user,s,IP,address,and,responds,with,available,information,such,as,city,country,name,specific,latitude,and,longitude,coordinates,and,a,corresponding,time,zone,The,ShinyGeoip,is,supported,by,Simon,Samtleben,at,Nekudo,com,and,depends,on,the,GeoLite,Database,The,API,is,accessed,via,GET,requests,over,HTTP,and,responds,with,a,JSON,encoded,string,The,API,can,be,viewed,as,an,open,source,project,on,GitHub